On a 3000 DPS mob, your rune goes poof in less than a second.  In 18 seconds, your MoM HP soak has run empty, and you are OOM (you might do marginally better if you manage to channel another rune).
<br />

<br />
Meanwhile, you aren't much better a tank than a plate tank is, and definately worse than a warrior with /defensive up.
<br />

<br />
It takes you 9 minutes to regain your empty mana pool.
<br />

<br />
Admittedly, the end/mana tank versions might impact raid balance.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
