                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">i just wanted to mention, while these changes will prolly never happen(ive lost faith in any meaningful changes actually coming about, especially if they require work), the core ideas you present are imo the most balanced, and best solution ive seen to date.
<br />

<br />
