<br />
I like a lot of the idea of the buff shift, but it does have some impact on soloin and we need to think of how to adress that to try to reflect balance as they have it now.
<br />
the mez softcap's long overdue.  Aside from stuns, i cant think of any core ability any class has that's level dependant like mezes.  Keep in mind the effect this will have on aiding interrupting casters(im not too concerned about  it, just wanna make sure its not ignored, tryin to point out the small areas that balance is shifted with your changes)
<br />
The rune focii are something they need to add, and i htink sanguine pres items should be more available, and there should be sanguine pres items for ppl of all diff gear lvls.(tho im not positive on that as i dont have a sang pres item myself, and it may be more unbalancing than i think)
<br />

<br />
I think your best idea tho is spreading out the mez responsabilities and bringing a need for CC back to the game.  i think this adresses the orignal reasons for the CC nerf without screwing the CC class out of its role.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
