</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Khyla the Apathetic wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">the mez softcap's long overdue. Aside from stuns, i cant think of any core ability any class has that's level dependant like mezes. Keep in mind the effect this will have on aiding interrupting casters(im not too concerned about it, just wanna make sure its not ignored, tryin to point out the small areas that balance is shifted with your changes) </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
